<br>
EG: Level 24 pets could dual wield, but onyl the highest level summons. Same with level 39 pets: only the top 4 level pets would have the 30 hp/tick regen. Now all pets are the highest level summon, they al will regen/dual weild with/without weapons.<br>
<br>
I don't know whether it's level 39 or 44 because I always equip my epts with weapons so I can have an elemental defender on their back slot. I also equip coldstones for the extra AC and if without weapons the may end up in the melee slots.<br>
<br>
If you chain cast pets then this difference is essential for you, but since I don't, I don't know <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Mage Compendium says Level 39 though, so I'd go with that. <p>Majishia Vie <Wyrd Angles>
