<br>
In fact, you've hit the reason why I was asking - I've been practicing chain casting as I like the theory and mana efficiency.  Casting 200 mana for a new pet kind of makes healing it or nuking the mob seem a waste of mana.<br>
<br>
A friend of mine described chain casting as the mage's equivilent of a root/DoT which I liked.  Made me re-think the whole chain cast philosophy.<br>
<br>
Anyway - I think I'd only want to chain cast a pet that could dual wield without weps.<br>
<br>
Canelin.<br>
